ygData.msgSnippet: Wow, I loved Brell.  If my characters havent been axed I still have some there. I promised my son when he turned 13 he could play EQ so he set up his account
ygData.messageBody:
Wow, I loved Brell.  If my characters havent' been axed I still have some there.
 
I promised my son when he turned 13 he could play EQ so he set up his account last night.  He has a friend on Xev so I'll reactivate my acct. to play with him (gotta stay in the loop with my teen).  But I WILL NOT GET READDICTED!  Actually, my life is very full now and I don't think I have time to get readdicted.  It's what I'll do when I have custody (yeah, well... that's another story) and we want to play together.
 
Trying Anarchy Online too, as long as I'm at it - see what it's like.  I hear you can actually have a productive play session in only an hour so it may work out better for me.
 
Gonna try enchanter... Luna, HELP! 
 
Ice

Well, I am a 44th Dark Elf Shadowknight on Brell Serilis.  I am one of
Violent Harvest's three leaders.  In fact, all three of us are RL females.  
My character is male, but that is only because I really enjoy playing men.  
Don't know why, I just have more fun being an aggressive male figure,
particularly an evil one like Khasirath.

I never saw the EQ Women Site, but would be interested in the URL if someone
has it...

So if any of your are on Brell, or stop by, send me a tell! I'm hunting
mostly in Velious right now, but will probably develop wanderlust soon.

Shadows guard thee,

Khasirath S`Therik
Knight of Innoruuk's Will
Thresher of the Violent Harvest
